snippet.title: Forgotten but Unbroken - Game Teaser
snippet.description: Hello guys. Before we leave to Gamescom 2022, we'd like to share with you our latest gameteaser. We hope you enjoy it. If you do, please give us a like/follow on our social networks ( https://www.facebook.com/CenturionDevelopments ,  https://twitter.com/Centurion_Dev ). Growing community is our best ammunition. Thanks a lot.   #xcom #ww2 #forgottenbutunbroken #turnbased #strategy
